when you're someone so special to me?

277
00:19:06,397 --> 00:19:07,067
Moo,

278
00:19:07,287 --> 00:19:08,347
you do realize

279
00:19:08,907 --> 00:19:10,907
that not everyone on Earth

280
00:19:15,997 --> 00:19:19,147
