as they are on the outside like I am.

281
00:19:20,047 --> 00:19:22,723
Plus, there's no one who has
better intention toward you than I am...

282
00:19:22,747 --> 00:19:23,547
Enough.

283
00:19:23,647 --> 00:19:25,687
You full-on fawn over yourself
every chance you get.

284
00:19:28,307 --> 00:19:29,307
Come on.

285
00:19:29,527 --> 00:19:30,547
Go take a shower.

286
00:19:30,987 --> 00:19:33,187
We have something to take care of today.

287
00:19:35,227 --> 00:19:37,747
I need to buy soy sauce from Tim's.

288
00:19:38,787 --> 00:19:39,787
It's 'Toy's.'

289
00:19:39,987 --> 00:19:41,387
Right, my bad.

290
00:19:50,807 --> 00:19:54,447
(How were you guys last night?)

291
00:19:55,497 --> 00:19:56,717
Last night...

292
00:19:58,687 --> 00:19:59,687
Yeah...

293
00:20:02,877 --> 00:20:04,327
