294
00:20:11,397 --> 00:20:12,977
Would you like to try our new recipe?

295
00:20:21,797 --> 00:20:22,887
Are you talking to me?

296
00:20:23,197 --> 00:20:25,427
Well, there are only two of us here.

297
00:20:31,927 --> 00:20:33,107
It's just that

298
00:20:33,467 --> 00:20:35,387
I made a new recipe.

299
00:20:35,787 --> 00:20:37,867
If it's not too much to ask,

300
00:20:38,407 --> 00:20:39,547
would you taste it for me?

301
00:20:50,297 --> 00:20:51,307
Mm!

302
00:20:51,947 --> 00:20:53,147
That's pretty good.

303
00:20:53,327 --> 00:20:55,387
The taste is quite well-balanced.

304
00:20:55,507 --> 00:20:57,067
