305
00:20:57,507 --> 00:20:58,427
Some MSG.

306
00:20:58,467 --> 00:20:59,467
What?

307
00:21:00,627 --> 00:21:01,627
Just kidding.

308
00:21:02,067 --> 00:21:03,747
It's just our special fermented fruits.

309
00:21:05,927 --> 00:21:07,307
Well, well,

310
00:21:08,707 --> 00:21:09,947
