347
00:23:40,147 --> 00:23:41,267
Deep-fried whale meat...

348
00:23:43,327 --> 00:23:44,327
What are you doing?

349
00:23:45,467 --> 00:23:46,467
It's really windy here.

350
00:23:48,347 --> 00:23:49,347
I...

351
