461
00:30:27,227 --> 00:30:28,227
Mr. Fu.

462
00:30:28,667 --> 00:30:29,407
So...

463
00:30:29,447 --> 00:30:31,947
We are currently
accepting internship applications.

464
00:30:32,727 --> 00:30:33,657
There have been... uh...

465
00:30:33,677 --> 00:30:35,367
