466
00:30:35,407 --> 00:30:37,407
So I brought them here
for you to make a selection.

467
00:30:38,187 --> 00:30:39,187
Alright.

468
00:30:39,867 --> 00:30:40,907
I'll be sure to make one.

469
00:30:43,807 --> 00:30:44,807
Mr. Fu?

470
00:30:44,897 --> 00:30:45,587
Yes?

471
00:30:45,887 --> 00:30:47,667
Thank you for dinner.

472
00:30:48,127 --> 00:30:49,727
The staff said it was scrumptious

473
00:30:49,767 --> 00:30:51,707
