474
00:30:52,627 --> 00:30:53,627
Alright.

475
00:30:53,927 --> 00:30:56,197
It's nice that everyone likes it.

476
00:30:57,187 --> 00:30:57,777
Oh...

477
00:30:58,197 --> 00:31:00,047
Alright, if you'll excuse me.

478
00:32:18,547 --> 00:32:22,547
Moo, Moo, Moo, Moo-Moo,
Moo, Moo, Moo, Moo-Moo Jelly.

479
00:32:22,587 --> 00:32:25,817
Nice and chewy, sweet and playful.

480
00:32:25,897 --> 00:32:29,827
The goodness that everyone enjoys.

481
00:32:29,867 --> 00:32:34,327
Moo-Moo-Moo! Moo, Moo, Moo, Moo, Moo-Moo,
Moo, Moo, Moo, Moo-Moo Jelly.

482
00:32:34,387 --> 00:32:39,047
The goodness that your loved one
is waiting to chew, Moo-Moo Jelly.

483
00:32:41,107 --> 00:32:42,587
Jelly!

484
