512
00:33:53,107 --> 00:33:54,947
does this mean
you're back to your normal self?

513
00:33:55,667 --> 00:33:56,667
Yes.

514
00:33:57,027 --> 00:33:58,027
I...

515
00:33:58,247 --> 00:34:01,747
