538
00:36:00,147 --> 00:36:02,387
- But don't you want a wingman?
- Wingman...

539
00:36:02,747 --> 00:36:04,427
I'm here to teach you how to win Moo over.

540
00:36:04,627 --> 00:36:06,267
Just 2,000 baht per trick.

541
00:36:06,697 --> 00:36:07,697
2,000...

542
00:36:09,167 --> 00:36:10,187
Tee!

543
00:36:10,317 --> 00:36:11,597
Are you addicted to video games?

544
00:36:12,167 --> 00:36:13,367
Why do you need so much money?

545
00:36:13,547 --> 00:36:14,627
You wouldn't know.

546
00:36:14,727 --> 00:36:15,487
These days,

547
00:36:15,507 --> 00:36:17,427
